{"word":"ὁδαῖος","slug":"ὁδαῖος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n72001\" key=\"o(dai=os\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὁδ-αῖος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὁδός</etym>) <sense id=\"n72001.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἐνόδιος</ref></xr>, of Hermes, Id. (s.v.l.). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n72001.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁδαῖα, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>,</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that for which a merchant travels, merchandise</tr_> (obtained in exchange for his <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φόρτος</foreign> or first freight), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:163\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.163</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:445\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.445</biblScope> </bibl> ; though a Sch. explains it as <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἐφόδια</ref></xr>, Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">viaticum</tr_> ; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁδάω.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}